'''DA-1''' was a sentient controlled data [[Analysis droid/Legends|analysis droid]] onboard the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] ship [[Steadfast (carrier)|''Steadfast'']]. In [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]] DA-1 was one of the droids involved in the finding of a operational datacore on the [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] ''[[Gnisnal]]'' that allowed for the discovery of the [[Black Fleet]]. DA-1's controller was [[Makki]].

